726987f-a.title: Queens: Jamaica Avenue - 138th Place
726987f-a.text:
Jamaica Avenue, at 138th Place, showing the elevated station
of the B.M.T. subway, seen in an easterly direction from the S.E.
corner of 138th Street.
P. L. Sperr  View 1: January 28, 1931
NO REPRODUCTIONS  View 2: May 7, 1934
